Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.09,0:01:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.52,0:02:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊  都已经七月了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.42,0:03:00.50,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fad(0,500)\pos(102,386)}第六集{\fs32}{\alpha&HFF}\Naaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa{\alpha}Innocent\N{\fs0}赎罪的… 救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.79,0:03:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说只有我能理解你那些设定  这也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.88,0:03:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你也应该跟其他人说说话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.90,0:03:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了勇太之外
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.07,0:03:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也跟凸守  枯茗和丹生谷说话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.91,0:03:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话是没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.64,0:03:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其他人也…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.58,0:03:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太在班里能聊的也就只有我  丹生谷和一色而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.60,0:03:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.41,0:03:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把我跟你相提并论
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.07,0:03:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说我本来就不喜欢热闹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.03,0:03:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真麻烦  还是不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.28,0:03:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在目前的空间里  只有她们能识别我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.71,0:03:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富樫君很擅长画画呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.38,0:03:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个小鸟游同学画得好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会  会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.75,0:03:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.38,0:03:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富樫君有在画漫画吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.51,0:03:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.15,0:03:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中二病时期可没少画插图啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.74,0:03:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,画好了  超帅气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.60,0:03:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看  让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.02,0:03:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人  是富樫君吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在战斗中的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.98,0:04:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗中？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.91,0:04:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在濒死状态下拼尽全力放出的Dark Flame
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.34,0:04:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.92,0:04:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Flame？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.61,0:04:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不可大肆宣扬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Flame可是勇太最强的攻击魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.63,0:04:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.00,0:04:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.84,0:04:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何时何地都别掉以轻心  冒牌森大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.32,0:04:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许叫我森大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.27,0:04:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  丹生谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.78,0:04:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是熟人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.98,0:04:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.36,0:04:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来学妹也很爱戴你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.83,0:04:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.47,0:04:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.08,0:04:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干  干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.49,0:04:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下课之后有时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.37,0:04:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  你收到情书了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.29,0:04:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:04:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说你不是一直在期盼这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.28,0:05:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛这么慌张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.81,0:05:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为  人家没想到真的会收到嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.02,0:05:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卖什么萌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是因为吉他对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.01,0:05:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能被他人看上的  也就只有玩音乐这一点了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我都还不会弹啊  怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.24,0:05:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总  总之你先离我远点好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都被你吓坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.06,0:05:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是小和弦对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说女孩子的话  就一定是小三和弦对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.20,0:05:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么知识啊  给我冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.83,0:05:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.84,0:05:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好想想  问题一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.23,0:05:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个真的是情书吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.29,0:05:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.53,0:05:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题二  不是男生的恶作剧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:38.51,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fs36\shad0\bord0\fn方正准圆_GBK\b1\c&H8859C7&\pos(808,220)}一色君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:38.51,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fs36\shad0\bord0\fn方正准圆_GBK\b1\c&H8859C7&\pos(785,335)}这周周六放学后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:38.51,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fs36\shad0\bord0\fn方正准圆_GBK\b1\c&H8859C7&\pos(781,456)}在银杏树下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:38.51,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fs36\shad0\bord0\fn方正准圆_GBK\b1\c&H8859C7&\frz348.763\pos(739,543)}等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.86,0:05:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看看这圆体字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这周周六放学后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.03,0:05:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在银杏树下等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.41,0:05:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧  没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.48,0:05:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题三
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.60,0:05:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有可能是男生和女生合谋的恶作剧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.71,0:05:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是有信任障碍吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.69,0:05:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个就说来话长了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.94,0:05:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得会是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.31,0:06:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说信上写着是同班同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.35,0:06:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最关键的名字却没写啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.73,0:06:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么头绪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.82,0:06:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枚方  生天目  街风
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.77,0:06:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啦  都不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.84,0:06:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  一定要说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.99,0:06:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的话？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.00,0:06:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹生谷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.55,0:06:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想啊  丹生谷她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.79,0:06:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我们视线对上的时候会对我笑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.12,0:06:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性格也挺认真成熟的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.76,0:06:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以会被玩音乐的男生的野性所吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.44,0:06:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能不可能不可能不可能不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.10,0:06:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你这么肯定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.51,0:06:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这个我可以断言
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.67,0:06:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.99,0:06:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  难道说你已经和丹生谷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是真不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.19,0:06:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.14,0:06:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹生谷跟你怎么看都不配啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.12,0:06:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮不到你来说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.36,0:06:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之我想知道到底是谁给我写的信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  我就这样直接跑去到处问也不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.87,0:06:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只能靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.54,0:07:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当做当天的惊喜不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  你觉得我对着初次见面的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能灵活地随机应变吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对会紧张到搞砸的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.90,0:07:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.91,0:07:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别自信满满地说自己没自信啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗笼罩着我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.51,0:07:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗之力无疑正降临于我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.18,0:07:21.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当睡衣穿很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.81,0:07:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此  我也不认为这几个人会有头绪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿着这个出现的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要好好地自报身份
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.25,0:07:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪王真眼掌控者  结社第零号
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸟游六花
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.45,0:07:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪王真眼之随从
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷霆战锤掌控者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.01,0:07:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结社第零号  凸守早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.54,0:07:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战栗的  暗夜梦魇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.54,0:07:43.06,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&HFF}aaaaaa{\alpha}Night Siesta
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结社第零号  五月七日枯茗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.74,0:07:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.77,0:07:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这编号还有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.79,0:07:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然编号里还是零最帅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.40,0:07:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了零之外不作他选
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:07:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不是很明白但感觉很帅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.14,0:07:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底谁最适合这个编号  在此一决胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.91,0:08:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正有此意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.24,0:08:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能这么玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.27,0:08:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.73,0:08:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐你别也跟着起哄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是富樫君不也穿着吗  在衬衫里面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.37,0:08:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦  这只是碰巧没别的衣服穿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.41,0:08:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦勇太  你穿了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.28,0:08:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这白痴中二病小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.76,0:08:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.37,0:08:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来必须要给白痴长长记性才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.47,0:08:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是  纯白之水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.40,0:08:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经把它充分加热了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.09,0:08:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你好好品尝它的醇香和甜美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.91,0:08:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是恶魔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.15,0:08:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  在这里凸守才是黑暗阵营的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.65,0:08:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋  是天使吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.43,0:08:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.16,0:08:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  快喝  快给我喝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.99,0:08:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.37,0:08:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  小凸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.04,0:08:56.39,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快喝快喝快喝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:08:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.50,0:08:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  丹生谷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.91,0:09:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么  老娘现在很忙  给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.32,0:09:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.78,0:09:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事啊  烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.70,0:09:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢妨碍我的话连你也一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.47,0:09:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀一色君  有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.46,0:09:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  我来找勇太商量点事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这样啊  吓我一跳…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你胆子还不小呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.19,0:09:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的纯白之水已经被消灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看好了  冒牌森大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.40,0:09:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我把你送至前往无限力量地平线的死亡之旅！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.02,0:09:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.61,0:09:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子还挺有趣的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.90,0:09:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『黑暗圣典』七色摹本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.37,0:09:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三章第一节
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.24,0:09:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当精灵的细语
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.25,0:09:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与光与水的思念传达给我们之时
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.64,0:09:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色的世界将被开启
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.56,0:09:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四百年来  一直注视着这世界的我能够明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界最需要的就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.90,0:10:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口啊  我不想听到这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.84,0:10:06.29,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.84,0:10:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是冒牌货
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.08,0:10:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到真身的真言之后精神崩溃了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.26,0:10:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小森大人振作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许叫我森大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.97,0:10:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹生谷  你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.68,0:10:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是敢把刚才看到的告诉班里的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.19,0:10:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会咒死你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.76,0:10:32.24,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.73,0:10:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风  要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.33,0:10:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.91,0:11:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说是恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会  说不定真的是女生写的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.98,0:11:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.67,0:11:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看出是谁写的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.16,0:11:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个倒不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.26,0:11:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有可能是一见钟情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.30,0:11:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得有可能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.71,0:11:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.21,0:11:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  能不能和这个女生顺利交往
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就看你接下来的表现了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  今天看到的你已经忘记了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.18,0:11:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太好了  再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.40,0:11:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是呢  你要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.39,0:11:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我尽力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.98,0:11:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了到时候不管是谁来都能应付
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.02,0:11:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在周六前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.14,0:11:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会将班上每个女生的情景都模拟一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.07,0:11:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做到万无一失
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.42,0:11:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.74,0:11:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  在可爱女生选拔赛中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.76,0:11:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经从男生们手上搞到了全班女生的资料
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.77,0:12:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始还不迟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.42,0:12:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一色
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.36,0:12:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间紧迫  我先上车了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.09,0:12:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回头见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.83,0:12:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  要回去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.50,0:12:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太  把手给我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.32,0:12:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.05,0:12:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:12:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.56,0:12:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在解读风声
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.32,0:12:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.89,0:13:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.10,0:13:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风儿很喧嚣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.68,0:13:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是电车的噪音啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.49,0:13:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,综上所述
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果猪俣同学捡到的这个小册子上写的都是事实的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.66,0:13:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就意味着  班上的男生擅自给女生们做过排名
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了  这下糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.21,0:13:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个时候掉的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天在车站的长椅上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.52,0:13:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过它的持有者还没有暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.85,0:13:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于这件事  我想听听各位男生的说法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.73,0:13:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米良君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.44,0:13:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:14:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米良君  你参与这个排名投票了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.45,0:14:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.19,0:14:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.22,0:14:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.99,0:14:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.50,0:14:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.25,0:14:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.55,0:14:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙啊  真的不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.53,0:14:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.88,0:14:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这个主谋被揪出来是迟早的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那还没开始的恋爱就要结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.12,0:14:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快想想  必须想个办法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.47,0:14:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.51,0:14:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得应该问问富樫君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.46,0:14:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  他可是班长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.39,0:14:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富樫君  你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.77,0:14:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.81,0:14:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.19,0:14:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.99,0:14:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.69,0:14:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.58,0:14:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说两句吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.54,0:14:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我干的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.18,0:14:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个小册子是我写的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.25,0:14:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名次也是我排的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一色
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.02,0:15:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一色君  你说的是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.15,0:15:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  但请不要误会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有在班里搞过投票
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.15,0:15:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些全都是我一个人写的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.83,0:15:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我只是一时觉得好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.05,0:15:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和班里其他男生没有任何关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.11,0:15:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切都是我一个人的错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.89,0:15:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是该鼓掌的时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.50,0:15:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  这些全都是你一个人干的是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.42,0:15:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.19,0:15:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是曝光之后伤害了女生们也是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事已至此  我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.13,0:15:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定剃光头谢罪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一色  你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.21,0:15:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为男人  不这么做怎么能行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.40,0:15:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是光头…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:16:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  也不用做到那个地步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.51,0:16:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这是身为男人的担当啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.74,0:16:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.21,0:16:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个「舍生取帅」的作战有效果吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.35,0:16:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有为了保全男生们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把所有过错一肩扛的这份侠义
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.95,0:16:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.89,0:16:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎么处理你的脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.22,0:16:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  你是说剃光头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.37,0:16:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.49,0:16:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个嘛  只是为了显示我的觉悟啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.63,0:16:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  你不是说那是男人的担当吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.33,0:16:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家总不会真打算让我剃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.49,0:16:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家就是这么打算的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.38,0:16:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹生谷  你什么时候来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.71,0:16:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉你  女生们还在怀疑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.64,0:16:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴上说得再漂亮也没人会相信的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.11,0:16:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非一色君按照承诺做个了断
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.93,0:16:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了  这可是你自己提出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.21,0:17:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧  不是真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.49,0:17:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再问你一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.18,0:17:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要剃掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.27,0:17:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊  真心不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.83,0:17:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是我熬过初中三年的光头生活
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易攒下的一头秀发啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.10,0:17:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能愿意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.14,0:17:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明天就去道歉  求她们放过你的头发啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  如果那样做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.07,0:17:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不就彻底变成一个懦夫了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.03,0:17:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像丹生谷说的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.67,0:17:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我现在不做个了断的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.36,0:17:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班里的女生也好  给我写情书的女生也好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.06,0:17:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定都会当我是废柴的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.10,0:17:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  不仅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.33,0:17:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我那样说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.06,0:17:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班里的男生们会就再次遭到怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.78,0:17:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.56,0:17:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  发起投票的人本来就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.60,0:17:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己挖的坑自己来填
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.56,0:17:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是男人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.99,0:17:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.94,0:17:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是所谓的日本式切腹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.89,0:17:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.38,0:17:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也差不多啦  赶紧剃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.11,0:17:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这帮家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.52,0:17:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碍事了  给我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.93,0:18:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是结社的指挥部  所有权归
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.20,0:18:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.09,0:18:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.44,0:18:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My servant
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.99,0:18:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.63,0:18:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.56,0:18:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.34,0:18:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.29,0:18:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你为我做了那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入学典礼那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.54,0:18:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和你说上话真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.58,0:18:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的老爸35岁的时候就脱发了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗传下来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.12,0:18:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能摆弄头型的时间  也就只有二十来年了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.03,0:18:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这其中的三年  我已经以光头度过了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今却又要回到那样的生活  真是可笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.95,0:18:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一色… 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.55,0:18:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哭什么啊  勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  狠下心来剃光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.87,0:18:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你的手剃了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.45,0:18:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一色
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.88,0:19:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  大家这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.55,0:19:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被勇太封印了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.50,0:19:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.23,0:19:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.63,0:19:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My servants
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.01,0:19:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.93,0:19:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过现在一色的神经非常脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.06,0:19:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托大家了  能去给他打打气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.03,0:19:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.73,0:19:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了  我会赐予他魔力的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.81,0:19:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不太明白  不过交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.94,0:19:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.80,0:19:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开门之前  我再次提醒大家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.22,0:19:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对  不能笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.95,0:19:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.91,0:19:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩没听到我说什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.72,0:19:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打人家干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.96,0:19:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一色
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.66,0:19:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦… 哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.23,0:19:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想为你的勇气赐予力量  来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.88,0:19:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聚集在此的黑暗之力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.26,0:19:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵从吾之命令  祝福此人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.33,0:19:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.08,0:20:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫他…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.83,0:20:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这破坏力也太强了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样  「可爱女生选拔赛」事件算是告一段落
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.79,0:20:09.84,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别笑了  你们到底还有没有良心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.59,0:20:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  在银杏树之下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.66,0:20:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对情书女孩的现身还抱有一丝希望的一色
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.60,0:20:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎来了命运的星期六
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.47,0:20:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一色君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一色意外地得到了班里男生的狂热支持
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.06,0:20:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  写情书的人最后也没有出现啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.40,0:20:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹生谷  你真的不知道是谁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.92,0:20:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算知道了又有什么用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.02,0:20:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.98,0:20:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.13,0:20:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护男生而履行剃光头的诺言  这种气概还是不错的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.35,0:20:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定会有女生这么想哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.33,0:20:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.31,0:21:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你傻啊  怎么可能有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.12,0:21:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在耍我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.74,0:21:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.80,0:21:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在忍不住了  所以就…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了一色君  让我摸摸嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.93,0:21:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  你这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.74,0:21:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假  就要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.84,0:21:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  勇太你打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.62,0:21:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸他今年回不了日本
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.96,0:21:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们可能得去雅加达哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.80,0:21:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我考虑一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.86,0:21:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.24,0:21:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事要拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.97,0:21:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假期间我希望你能和六花一起过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.88,0:21:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.07,0:22:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天  来临了
